- (Europe/Central Asia) Uzbekistan;
- (Middle East/Africa) Kenya, Comoros, Republic of the Congo, Sierra Leone, Sudan, Somalia, Namibia, Palestine, Botswana, Madagascar, Libya, Liberia.

